{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u300eFix-mas\u300f is a top-view action game centered on Just Avoidance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">To fix a toy with Chris, the fairy of the Christmas gift factory</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Make a screw over the enemy's head with magic bullets and accurate evasion, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">rush it in and throw it in!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">not in-game english supported!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Fairy &quot;Chris&quot; to fix the toys</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">On Christmas Eve, misassembled toys started going crazy! Fairy Chris goes out to solve the mess with a screwdriver.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Cracking a toy with a screw</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">To defeat an enemy, you must first fire a magic bullet with a screwdriver to create a screw over your enemy's head!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">And rush towards the enemy and screw in the screw you've made!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Evading enemy attacks in a timely manner</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">When the enemy evades in time for an attack, bonus bullets fly away! Bonus bullets instantly create a single screw over the enemy's head.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Fixing Broken Toys</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you've broken the toy, now it's time to fix it again and wrap it up pretty!</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3424500/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738602355","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3424500/page.bg.jpg?t=1738602355","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3424500/d195d376e863a7573c1a254da6c7b20926a53c38/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738602355","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3424500/d195d376e863a7573c1a254da6c7b20926a53c38/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738602355","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u300eFix-mas\u300f is a top-view action game centered on Just Avoidance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">To fix a toy with Chris, the fairy of the Christmas gift factory</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Make a screw over the enemy's head with magic bullets and accurate evasion, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">rush it in and throw it in!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">not in-game english supported!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Fairy &quot;Chris&quot; to fix the toys</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">On Christmas Eve, misassembled toys started going crazy! Fairy Chris goes out to solve the mess with a screwdriver.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Cracking a toy with a screw</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">To defeat an enemy, you must first fire a magic bullet with a screwdriver to create a screw over your enemy's head!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">And rush towards the enemy and screw in the screw you've made!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Evading enemy attacks in a timely manner</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">When the enemy evades in time for an attack, bonus bullets fly away! Bonus bullets instantly create a single screw over the enemy's head.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Fixing Broken Toys</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you've broken the toy, now it's time to fix it again and wrap it up pretty!</p>","developers":["Be\ud3ed\ub825\uc8fc\uc758\uc790"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Casual","id":"4"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"Free To Play","id":"37"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3424500/header.jpg?t=1738602355","is_free":true,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257084605,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com